# Lumibud (Early Version - Lumaine)

## Overview
This repository contains an early version of Lumibud, a productivity and lifestyle web application designed to help users manage study planning, tasks, and daily routines.

This project represents the initial development phase, where core features and architecture were designed and tested.

## Features
- Task and study planning
- Basic UI structure
- Early data handling 

## Tech Stack
- JavaScript
- HTML/CSS

## Development Context
This version was later iterated into an improved version of Lumibud with enhanced features, usability, and performance.

## Future Improvements
- Improved UI/UX
- Authentication system
- Scalable backend architecture
